  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:1",
      "text": "Denoiser Highlights（降噪器亮点）：",
      "ascii_letters": 18,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:2",
      "text": "Machine Learning（机器学习降噪核心）-",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 8
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:4",
      "text": "Production Proven（制作验证）-",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:5",
      "text": "这项先进的 denoising technology（降噪技术）非常可靠，由 Disney Research 开发，并已在 Pixar、Walt Disney Animation Studios (WDAS) 和 Industrial Light and Magic 的制作中使用，证明了它的高效性。",
      "ascii_letters": 91,
      "cjk_chars": 34
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:6",
      "text": "Highest Fidelity（最高保真度）-",
      "ascii_letters": 15,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:8",
      "text": "Denosing the Luxo Ball（对 Luxo Ball 进行降噪）",
      "ascii_letters": 27,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:9",
      "text": "既然我们已经了解了一些 denoiser 的背景信息，现在就把它用于实践：在弹跳的 Luxo Ball animation 上测试 denoiser。该 animation 使用 XPU 渲染，并开启了 DOF 和 Motion Blur。denoiser mode 设置为 Cross Frame（因为我们正在渲染 animation）。",
      "ascii_letters": 89,
      "cjk_chars": 53
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:11",
      "text": "Pixel Variance",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:12",
      "text": "Min Samples",
      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
