      "ascii_letters": 10,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:14",
      "text": "Av. Frame Times（平均帧时间）",
      "ascii_letters": 12,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:16",
      "text": "IntialTest_wide.mov",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:17",
      "text": "IntialTest_cropped.mov",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:18",
      "text": "把它送入 RenderMan Denoiser 后，我们会得到一个 denoised version（已降噪版本），其质量等同于 adaptive threshold 为 .01 的渲染结果，非常适合 broadcast（广播级）输出。",
      "ascii_letters": 58,
      "cjk_chars": 38
    },
    {
      "item_id": "d809806b1e:20",
      "text": "Samples Made Simple",
      "ascii_letters": 17,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
